Package: ssmpower
Title: Power Analysis for the Structural Summary Method
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Kimberly", "Gilbert", , "kjg6@fordham.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0004-0373-6192"))
Description: Tools for power analysis and sample size planning for Structural 
    Summary Method (SSM) analyses of circumplex data. Provides functions to 
    calculate statistical power, determine required sample sizes, and generate 
    power curves for amplitude and elevation parameters. Based on effect size 
    benchmarks from Zimmermann and Wright (2017) <doi:10.1177/1073191115621795>.
